	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Also, if there's a .db that does bytes, there's probably a .dw that does words
<br />
<br />.dw label
<br />
<br />is simpler than
<br />
<br />.db &lt;label, &gt;label

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
